              </p>
            </div>
            <div
              class="flex flex-row items-start justify-items-start w-full py-5 gap-x-7.5 border-t border-t-porto1-divider md:pr-20"
            >
              <p class="text-porto1-p text-porto1-accent5">02</p>
              <p class="text-porto1-p">
                Get Everyone on the Same Page: Share easy-to-understand reports
                with your team.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div
              class="flex flex-row items-start justify-items-start w-full py-5 gap-x-7.5 border-t border-t-porto1-divider md:pr-20"
            >
              <p class="text-porto1-p text-porto1-accent5">03</p>
              <p class="text-porto1-p">
                Make Presentations Pop: Interactive maps and dashboards keep
                your audience engaged.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div
              class="flex flex-row items-start justify-items-start w-full py-5 gap-x-7.5 border-t border-t-porto1-divider md:pr-20"
            >
              <p class="text-porto1-p text-porto1-accent5">04</p>
              <p class="text-porto1-p">
                Your Global Snapshot: Get a quick, clear overview of your entire
                operation.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a
            href="https://www.figma.com/sites"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            aria-label="Learn more about Figma sites"
            class="w-fit gap-y-2.5 px-5.5 py-3.5 justify-center items-center bg-[#DFECC6] rounded-full text-center cursor-pointer text-porto1-link hover:text-white hover:bg-porto1-accent1/70"
          >
            Discover More
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-y-10 md:gap-y-5 fade-in-slow">
          <Image
            src={imgRoll}
            alt="Paper Roll"
            class="h-[385px] object-cover rounded-[30px] md:h-full"
            loading="lazy"
            fetchpriority="high"
          />
        </div>
      </section>
      <!-- End Features carousel -->

      <!-- Specifications table -->
      <section id="specs"
        class="flex flex-col gap-y-5 pb-30 border-t border-t-porto1-divider"
      >
        <div
          class="flex flex-col gap-y-10 px-4 py-20 md:p-20 lg:px-60 lg:py-20 fade-in"
        >
          <div
            class="flex flex-col justify-start items-center text-center gap-y-7.5 md:gap-y-10"
          >
            <h2 class="text-porto1-captions text-porto1-accent1">Specs</h2>
            <p class="text-porto1-h1">Why Choose Area?</p>
            <p class="text-porto1-p text-porto1-accent5">
              You need a solution that keeps up. That’s why we developed Area. A
