            </p>
            <a
              href="https://www.figma.com/sites"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              aria-label="Learn more about Figma sites"
              class="px-5.5 py-3.5 justify-center items-center bg-porto1-accent2 rounded-full text-center cursor-pointer text-porto1-link hover:text-white hover:bg-porto1-accent1/70"
